# Sample Songs Directory

This directory is for storing local audio files.

## Supported Formats
- MP3 (recommended)
- WAV
- OGG

## File Naming Convention
- Use descriptive names: "artist-title.mp3"
- Avoid spaces and special characters
- Keep file sizes under 10MB for best performance

## Usage
1. Add your audio files to this directory
2. Use the admin account to upload them to the application
3. Or reference them directly in the database.js file

## Sample Files
You can add your own music files here and they will be automatically included in the application when you reference them in the code.